                        </value>
                      </stat-item>
                      <stat-item>
                        <label>상담료</label>
                        <value>10만원</value>
                      </stat-item>
                    </stats>

                    <description class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">
                      정신적 피해 및 스트레스성 질환 전문. 대기업 산재 사건 다수 경험.
                    </description>
                  </content>

                  <actions class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                    <button href="/lawyers/4" class="primary-outline">상세 보기</button>
                    <button href="/lawyers/4/consult" class="secondary">상담 예약</button>
                  </actions>
                </div>
              </lawyer-card>

              <!-- 추가 노무사 카드들... -->
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

        <!-- 페이지네이션 -->
        <pagination class="mt-8">
          <page-info>총 127명 중 1-10명 표시</page-info>
          <page-controls>
            <button class="prev" disabled>이전</button>
            <page-number class="active">1</page-number>
            <page-number>2</page-number>
            <page-number>3</page-number>
            <span>...</span>
            <page-number>13</page-number>
            <button class="next">다음</button>
          </page-controls>
        </pagination>
      </container>
    </section>
  </layout>
</page>